::Striker::

Striker smiles, sweeping Spears off her feet and flying off toward the Ark, 
slowly at first and at a low altitude. He looks at her, not kissing her only 
because he had to look where he was going in order to avoid trees.

"Let's drop by at the Ark in case they need any help, eh?" he says, swirling 
to avoid a tree.
